title: [Coastal Cliffs]
description: The sea breeze is cool and salty, and it dampens your face as you look out over the breathtaking expanse of moonlit water below.  The sound of the waves crashing against the rocks roars in your ears.

The sea breeze is cool and salty, and it dampens your face as you look out over the breathtaking expanse of blue-green water below.  The sound of the waves crashing against the rocks roars in your ears.
